  • cn.sharesdk.demo使用的cn.sharesdk.framework.authorize中的类 
    类和说明
    AuthorizeAdapter
    the adapter of authorize page AuthorizeAdapter is the lifecycle listener of the authorize page( including AuthorizeAdapter.onCreate(), AuthorizeAdapter.onDestroy() etc. ), you can override and control the ui logic and events of the page by calling AuthorizeAdapter.getActivity(), AuthorizeAdapter.getTitleLayout(), AuthorizeAdapter.getWebBody(), AuthorizeAdapter.isNotitle() etc.
